					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10013569#post-4318454</guid>
				<title>Re: Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10013569/scp-4739#post-4318454</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2019 01:48:50 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DeRockProject</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>486453</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I had a simpler idea to just put the entire tale of Introductory Antimemetics into the SCP-4739 slot and it would be pretty appropriately mindscrew to click an SCP to get a tale.</p> <p>Despite being the 2nd tale in the series, it really is a good introduction to the whole series, as well as the concept of antimemetics.</p> 
				 	]]>
